22. The twenty ninth Canon forbids urging Parents to be Preſent when their Children
are baptized, and admitting them to Anſwer as Godfathers for their own Children;
and any Godfather to make any other Anſwer or ſpeech than the preſcribed.

6. So is it to feign falſly, that God calleth men to come out
from ſuch, and be ſeparate, becauſe he calleth them out of Babylon;
falſly adding to the Laws of God.
